<promed@promed.org>
[Both postings emphasize that they have found an organism which may be
_Naegleria fowleri_ and the second message uses the word "questionable." It
is important to realize that potential harmful microorganisms are an
integrated part of our environment. More information on the testing methods
used to identify _Naegleria fowleri_ in the water supply would be
appreciated. - Mod.EP]
